data.description: This contemporary single-family home in West Rosamond, built in 2020, offers a comfortable and modern living space. With 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, 2286 sq.ft of living area on a spacious 6969 square foot lot, it provides ample space for a growing family.Key features of this home include solar panels for energy efficiency, a tankless water heater for continuous hot water supply, and a large fenced backyard ready for your personal touches. The backyard boasts a concrete slab, stepping stone-style walkways, and some sod, offering a versatile outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment. Additionally, newer wood fencing surrounds three sides of the yard, providing privacy and security.The front yard features desert landscaping with a drip system, minimizing water consumption while maintaining an attractive curb appeal.The layout of the home is thoughtfully designed, with the kitchen, living room, dining area, and a convenient half bath located downstairs. All four bedrooms are situated upstairs, providing privacy and separation from the main living areas. The main bedroom includes an ensuite bathroom and large walk-in closet, while the other three bedrooms share another full bathroom.Conveniently located near freeway, shopping centers and schools, this home offers both comfort and practicality for modern family living in the West Rosamond area. With its contemporary features and potential for personalization, it presents an excellent opportunity for buyers seeking a move-in ready home with room to add their own finishing touches.
